Hi,
I'm an indie developer who just launched MeepleUp, a free app that helps tabletop gaming groups coordinate. It handles RSVPs, owned game title browsing and voting, and event messaging all in one place.
Gaming groups that you host will probably like it. Please visit https://meepleup.com to learn more, or just dive right in and download "MeepleUp" on the App Store or Google Play.
Thank you so much for any feedback you can provide. I've spent over a thousand hours building this app. It would mean so much to me to get it in the hands of people who might appreciate it.
Sincerely,
Rhys Smoker
